714182f-a.title: Manhattan: 65th Street (East) - Madison Avenue
714182f-a.text:
45 to 57 East 65th Street, north side, east from a point midway
between Madison and Park Aves., and to the latter, showing prominently
the home of President Franklin Delano Roosevelt and his mother, Mrs.
Sarah Delano Roosevelt, at No. 47-49 (balcony thereon).
January 2, 1938.
George D. Chinn.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
